      "source": [
        "### a. What does `perc` mean?"
      ],
      "id": "12098b8b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| code-fold: true\n",
        "\n",
        "alt.Chart(jobs_url).mark_line(point=True).encode(\n",
        "    x=\"year:O\",\n",
        "    y=\"sum(perc):Q\",\n",
        "    color=\"sex:N\"\n",
        ").properties(width=400, height=200, title=\"Sum of perc by Year and Sex\")"
      ],
      "id": "8a942609",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "The sum of `perc` for men and women is close to 1.0 each year. This means `perc` is the proportion of the **total population** working in that job, not within each sex.\n",
        "\n",
        "### b. Scatterplot with 4 year facets"
      ],
      "id": "0ae4f22f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| code-fold: true\n",
        "\n",
        "alt.Chart(jobs_url).transform_filter(\n",
        "    \"datum.year == 1850 || datum.year == 1950 || datum.year == 1980 || datum.year == 2000\"\n",
        ").transform_pivot(\n",
        "    \"sex\", groupby=[\"job\", \"year\"], value=\"perc\"\n",
        ").mark_point().encode(\n",
        "    x=alt.X(\"men:Q\", title=\"Men\", axis=alt.Axis(format=\".0%\")),\n",
        "    y=alt.Y(\"women:Q\", title=\"Women\", axis=alt.Axis(format=\".0%\")),\n",
        "    tooltip=[\"job:N\", \"men:Q\", \"women:Q\"],\n",
        "    column=\"year:O\"\n",
        ").properties(width=200, height=200)"
      ],
      "id": "4bd86f36",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### c. Percentage within each sex"
      ],
      "id": "6c0113b4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| code-fold: true\n",
        "\n",
        "filtered = jobs[jobs[\"year\"].isin([1850, 1950, 1980, 2000])].copy()\n",
        "totals = filtered.groupby([\"year\", \"sex\"])[\"count\"].transform(\"sum\")\n",
        "filtered[\"pct\"] = filtered[\"count\"] / totals\n",
        "\n",
        "alt.Chart(filtered).transform_pivot(\n",
        "    \"sex\", groupby=[\"job\", \"year\"], value=\"pct\"\n",
        ").mark_point().encode(\n",
        "    x=alt.X(\"men:Q\", title=\"% of Men\", axis=alt.Axis(format=\".0%\")),\n",
        "    y=alt.Y(\"women:Q\", title=\"% of Women\", axis=alt.Axis(format=\".0%\")),\n",
        "    tooltip=[\"job:N\", \"men:Q\", \"women:Q\"],\n",
        "    column=\"year:O\"\n",
        ").properties(width=200, height=200)"
      ],
      "id": "ff46b6c2",
